# Per-game data and games manifests live outside git: too large for GitHub
# (~7.5 GB total). To rebuild the labeled parquets you need to obtain these
# out-of-band or regenerate them from raw inputs (see README "Rebuilding
# datasets from scratch").
data/self_collected/per_game_data/
data/self_collected/games.csv
data/telonex/per_game_data/
data/telonex/games.csv
data/telonex/metadata/
data/telonex/cache/*
# but ship the small JSON caches so fresh clones get a warm start
!data/telonex/cache/kickoff_times.json
!data/telonex/cache/market_ids.json

# Raw WebSocket logs and discovered-markets CSV — produced by data_collection/.
data/raw_ws_logs/
data_collection/markets/

# Local rebuild outputs.
/tmp_*
